# ⚠️ TEAM WORKFLOW (READ BEFORE CODING)

## How We Work (Required)

Pull repo → create your own branch → only work inside your assigned folder.

DO NOT push directly to `main`.

### Example branches
- feature/frontend-ui
- feature/collector-stream
- feature/api-fastapi
- feature/model-training

Each teammate works ONLY inside their folder unless coordinated with the team.

This prevents merge conflicts and broken builds during the hackathon.

